<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Counter Offer - {{auctionTitle}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .counter-offer-box {
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px solid #667eea;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 2em;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #667eea;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #667eea;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #5a67d8;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Counter Offer Received</h1>
        <p>You have received a counter offer for your auction</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{firstName}},</h2>
        
        <p>The seller of <strong>{{auctionTitle}}</strong> has made you a counter offer.</p>
        
        <div class="counter-offer-box">
            <h3>Counter Offer Amount</h3>
            <div class="amount">${{counterAmount}}</div>
            <p>Please review this offer and respond accordingly.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>You can accept or reject this counter offer by clicking the button below:</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="{{responseUrl}}" class="btn">Respond to Counter Offer</a>
        </div>
        
        <p><strong>Important:</strong> This counter offer will expire if not responded to within a reasonable time.</p>
        
        <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The Tap2Win Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent from Tap2Win Auction Platform</p>
        <p>Â© 2025 Tap2Win. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
